{"tid":1492284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國準備58萬五毛出兵西方網路","createTime":"2019-08-20T18:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T18:59:12.000Z","uid":251269,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a0425f1f93c9310a1b3b3d8e8b9ddd7bf03fdae1","tid":1492284,"uid":251269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"中國啱啱比twitter同facebook封咗幾百個account 係外國媒體開始有啲輿論<br />\n而家仲要俾人發現原來前幾日先啱啱又用124萬人仔買咗58萬嘅account嚟大量打資訊戰<br />\n習敗北係咪真係以為啲外國人on9㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家快啲post上reddit同其他外國媒體煲大佢 提醒外國人要小心五毛<br />\n最好令到twitter直接terminate曬呢58萬個account 咁就可以搞到中國又要再洗錢買account <br />\n無曬維穩資金變相加速支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家國際戰線要食住個勢上 勢要令到全球排華 令全世界都見到中國幾邪惡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSMpYy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSMpYy2.jpg&h=86e9a26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrZbDy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrZbDy2.jpg&h=19622ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ccgp.gov.cn/cggg/dfgg/zbgg/201908/t20190816_12699714.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccgp.gov.cn%2Fcggg%2Fdfgg%2Fzbgg%2F201908%2Ft20190816_12699714.htm&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=2dcef706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ccgp.gov.cn/cggg/dfgg/zbgg/201908/t20190816_12699714.htm</a>"},{"pid":"322e44bf6c0fe52a487ad0f504ae230181ed862e","tid":1492284,"uid":123364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ddfb102ad99e12d1bf24ae423a977212f6077f9","tid":1492284,"uid":123205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:34:07.000Z","msg":"條數咁公開透明既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0775bf95f6372196bf72a8235a13d974ad52f102","tid":1492284,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike